<li class='cover' id='bookCover_3428935'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/3428935-the-warded-man"><img alt="The Warded Man (Demon Cycle, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1354571949l/3428935._SX98_.jpg" />
